        {
            "id": 6322406,
            "title": "華通、燿華亮燈！太空資料中心題材延燒　南亞科出關量價齊揚，下一檔熱門股都在這！？",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><a href=\"https://www.sinotrade.com.tw/richclub/hotopic/-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80%E8%82%A1TOP10-%E8%8F%AF%E9%80%9A-%E7%87%BF%E8%8F%AF%E9%9B%99%E6%BC%B2%E5%81%9C--%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E7%88%86PCB-%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E7%A7%91%E5%87%BA%E9%97%9C%E9%87%8F%E5%83%B9%E9%BD%8A%E6%8F%9A-6976b352e4a2e426570100dd?strProd=0213&amp;strWeb=0090&amp;utm_source=richclub&amp;utm_medium=textbanner&amp;utm_campaign=trade2?strProd=0213&amp;strWeb=0090&amp;utm_source=richclub&amp;utm_medium=textbanner&amp;utm_campaign=trade2\"><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6322406/l/c1c4b29bee6d4da144efaf54652f70e5.jpg\"/></a></figure></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6322406/l/3bd65a443478dddf4846b22266fac5f9.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">華通、燿華亮燈！太空資料中心題材延燒　南亞科出關量價齊揚，下一檔熱門股都在這！？(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://www.sinotrade.com.tw/richclub/hotopic/-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80%E8%82%A1TOP10-%E8%8F%AF%E9%80%9A-%E7%87%BF%E8%8F%AF%E9%9B%99%E6%BC%B2%E5%81%9C--%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E7%88%86PCB-%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E7%A7%91%E5%87%BA%E9%97%9C%E9%87%8F%E5%83%B9%E9%BD%8A%E6%8F%9A-6976b352e4a2e426570100dd?strProd=0213&amp;strWeb=0090&amp;utm_source=richclub&amp;utm_medium=textbanner&amp;utm_campaign=trade2?strProd=0213&amp;strWeb=0090&amp;utm_source=richclub&amp;utm_medium=textbanner&amp;utm_campaign=trade2\">回原文看完整新聞熱門股排行!!! \\\\ 快來點 //</a></p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>一、盤勢分析 (1/26)</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>今日台股盤面呈現「強者恆強、弱者修正」的劇烈分化格局，資金高度集中於具備「實質訂單」與「漲價題材」的族群。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>首先，<strong>低軌衛星與 PCB 族群</strong>成為盤面最強勢的焦點。隨著 SpaceX 密訪台灣供應鏈及馬斯克「太空資料中心」題材發酵，市場資金瘋狂湧入「純度高」的供應鏈。華通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2313-TW</a>)<strong> 與</strong>燿華 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2367:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2367\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2367-TW</a>) 雙雙亮燈漲停，顯示法人對於其技術護城河與訂單能見度的高度認同。這股熱潮也外溢至高階封裝與 AI 伺服器相關 PCB 個股，欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>) 亦獲資金青睞，整體族群氣勢如虹。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>其次，<strong>記憶體族群</strong>在報價上揚的超級週期下，多頭火種未滅。南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 處置出關首日即展現強勁吸金力，股價沿 5 日線走揚；群聯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8299:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8299\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8299-TW</a>)<strong> 則因切入企業級 AI 市場，市值大增千億，成為櫃買市場的中流砥柱。然而，投資人需留意個股的籌碼變化，如</strong>力積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6770:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6770\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6770-TW</a>) 遭外資大舉調節，股價面臨修正壓力；金寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2312:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2312\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2312-TW</a>) 則因衛星業務暫停而重挫，顯示在題材熱炒下，基本面的變化將直接主導股價走勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>二、個股熱度 TOP10</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>TOP10 </strong><strong>燿華 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2367:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2367\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2367-TW</a>)</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>熱度觀察：</strong> 低軌衛星與高毛利 PCB 題材，強勢漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>動態說明：</strong> 結合 SpaceX 訂單與高階 LCP/RF 板材優勢，受惠全球 PCB 產值創高預期。股價以漲停姿態躍居成交前段班，是短線資金追逐的最強指標。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>TOP9 </strong><strong>金寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2312:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2312\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2312-TW</a>)</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>熱度觀察：</strong> 低軌衛星業務暫停引發股價重挫，但 SSD 代工需求強勁。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>動態說明：</strong> 雖然管理層表示衛星業務短期受阻，但受惠記憶體大爆發，SSD 產能擴充翻倍，加上切入 AI 伺服器電源，長線轉型題材仍在。短線需消化利空賣壓，靜待量縮止穩。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>TOP8 </strong><strong>力積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6770:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6770\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6770-TW</a>)</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>熱度觀察：</strong> 外資賣超冠軍，股價面臨調節壓力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>動態說明：</strong> 雖受惠電子需求回溫，但外資單日大賣逾 5 萬張，籌碼面顯著轉弱。股價處於高檔換手階段，需觀察是否能守住重要支撐，操作宜保守。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>TOP7 </strong><strong>旺宏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2337:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2337\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2337-TW</a>)</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>熱度觀察：</strong> 關稅利空淡化，股價 V 型反轉。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>動態說明：</strong> 展現強勁抗跌韌性，雖然早盤受關稅消息衝擊，但隨後強勢翻紅。在記憶體報價上揚趨勢下，市場看好其特殊型 Flash 的利基優勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><strong>TOP6 </strong><strong>群創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3481:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3481\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3481-TW</a>)</strong></em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>熱度觀察：</strong> 外資大買中止連賣，成交量居高不下。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>動態說明：</strong> FOPLP 切入 SpaceX 與 AI 供應鏈題材持續吸金，外資態度轉多。惟股價走勢相對溫吞，顯示上方套牢賣壓仍需時間消化。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://www.sinotrade.com.tw/richclub/hotopic/-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80%E8%82%A1TOP10-%E8%8F%AF%E9%80%9A-%E7%87%BF%E8%8F%AF%E9%9B%99%E6%BC%B2%E5%81%9C--%E5%A4%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E5%95%86%E6%A9%9F%E5%BC%95%E7%88%86PCB-%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E7%A7%91%E5%87%BA%E9%97%9C%E9%87%8F%E5%83%B9%E9%BD%8A%E6%8F%9A-6976b352e4a2e426570100dd?strProd=0213&amp;strWeb=0090&amp;utm_source=richclub&amp;utm_medium=textbanner&amp;utm_campaign=trade2?strProd=0213&amp;strWeb=0090&amp;utm_source=richclub&amp;utm_medium=textbanner&amp;utm_campaign=trade2\">回原文看前五名熱門股是哪些!!! \\\\ 快來點 //</a></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\">本公司所推薦分析之個別有價證券<br/>\n無不當之財務利益關係 以往之績效不保證未來獲利<br/>\n投資人應獨立判斷 審慎評估並自負投資風險</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
